lead_paragraph: Cyprus’s finance minister says the island nation is on track to conclude its multibillion-euro rescue program on time this March, almost three years after receiving the lifeline.
snippet: Cyprus’s finance minister says the island nation is on track to conclude its multibillion-euro rescue program on time this March, almost three years after receiving the lifeline.

headline.main: Cyprus Is Expected to Conclude Its Bailout Deal as Scheduled
headline.print_headline: Cyprus Is Expected to Conclude Its Bailout Deal as Scheduled

abstract: Harris Georgiades, finance minister for Cyprus, says nation will complete its multibillion-euro rescue program, initiated in 2013 bailout deal, on time in March.
